<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>66</hymn_number>
<author>In Dulci Jubilo</author>
<title>Ry olona o, avia! FFPM66</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ry olona ô, avia !
 Ry tany, mifalia !
 Mba henoy ny teninay ;
 Teraka ny Tomponay ;
 Ao an-tranon'omby ao,
 Handeha, mitsaoka Azy izao
 Teraka ny Tompo !
 Teraka Jeso !

[V2]
 Ry olona ô, avia !
 Ry tany mifalia !
 Mba henoy, ry havanay !
 Misy zaza hitanay
 Zanak'Andriamanitra
 Hamoha indray ny lanitra.
 Teraka ny Tompo !
 Teraka Jeso !

[V3]
 Ry kristiana ô, hobio,
 Fa afaka hianao anio;
 Resy izao ny rafinao,
 Afaka ota hianao,
 Fahasoavan-dehibe
 No ho anjaranao anie ;
 Teraka ny Tompo !
 Teraka Jeso.</lyrics>
</song>